## 🔧 Troubleshooting

| Masalah | Solusi |
|---------|--------|
| AI tidak merespons | Cek ANTHROPIC_API_KEY sudah diset |
| "Method not allowed" | Pastikan netlify.toml ada di root folder |
| Landing page tidak muncul | Pastikan `public/index.html` ada |
| AI error "quota exceeded" | Top-up credit di console.anthropic.com |

